## 1. Current Codebase Deep Analysis

### 1.1 Project Identity

| Field | Value |
|-------|-------|
| **Project Name** | ELMS — Employee Leave Management System |
| **Current Stack** | React 19, Vite 8, Tailwind CSS 4, React Router 7 |
| **Architecture** | Frontend-only SPA with mock data |
| **Persistence** | `localStorage` (no database) |
| **Authentication** | Simulated (user-selector, no password/JWT) |
| **Build Tool** | Vite 8 with React Compiler (Babel plugin) |
| **Deployment** | None (dev server only) |

