| localStorage Persistence | ✅ Working | Survives page refresh |

### 1.4 Critical Gaps for Production

> [!CAUTION]
> The current project is a **UI prototype only**. Below is everything missing to ship to market.

| Gap | Severity | Impact |
|-----|----------|--------|
| **No Backend/API** | 🔴 Critical | Data lives in browser only, no persistence across devices |
| **No Real Authentication** | 🔴 Critical | Anyone can log in as any user, no passwords or tokens |
| **No Database** | 🔴 Critical | localStorage is volatile and per-browser |
| **No Authorization Middleware** | 🔴 Critical | API endpoints can be called by anyone |
| **No Input Sanitization** | 🔴 Critical | XSS and injection attack vectors |
| **No Password Hashing** | 🔴 Critical | Passwords must never be stored in plain text |
| **No Email/Notifications** | 🟡 High | Users have no way to get notified outside the app |
| **No Employee Management** | 🟡 High | Can't add/remove/edit employees |
| **No Department/Team Structure** | 🟡 High | Flat structure, no reporting hierarchy |
| **No Leave Policies Engine** | 🟡 High | Hardcoded leave types, no accrual/carry rules |
| **No Calendar View** | 🟠 Medium | No visual representation of leave schedules |
| **No File Attachments** | 🟠 Medium | Can't upload medical certificates etc. |
| **No Pagination** | 🟠 Medium | Tables will crash with 1000+ records |
| **No Testing** | 🟡 High | Zero unit/integration/e2e tests |
| **No CI/CD** | 🟡 High | No automated build/deploy pipeline |
| **No Error Boundaries** | 🟠 Medium | App crashes on any render error |
| **No Logging/Monitoring** | 🟠 Medium | No observability in production |
| **No Mobile Responsiveness** | 🟠 Medium | Sidebar layout breaks on mobile |
| **No Internationalization (i18n)** | 🟢 Low | English only |
| **No Accessibility (a11y)** | 🟢 Low | Missing ARIA labels, keyboard nav |

