## 3. Backend Design & API Blueprint

### 3.1 Tech Stack

| Layer | Technology | Why |
|-------|-----------|-----|
| Runtime | Node.js 22 LTS | Same language as frontend, huge ecosystem |
| Framework | Express.js 5 | Battle-tested, flexible, lightweight |
| ORM | Prisma 6 | Type-safe, auto-generated queries, migrations |
| Database | PostgreSQL 16 | Relational, ACID, best for structured leave data |
| Cache | Redis 7 | Session cache, rate limiting, real-time |
| Auth | JWT (jsonwebtoken) + bcrypt | Industry standard, stateless auth |
| Validation | Zod | Schema validation matching TypeScript types |
| File Upload | Multer + S3/MinIO | Medical certs, documents |
| Email | Nodemailer + SendGrid | Transactional emails |
| WebSocket | Socket.io | Real-time leave status notifications |
| AI | Google Gemini API | Smart leave analysis, chatbot |

### 3.2 REST API Endpoints

#### Auth
```
POST   /api/auth/register            # Employee self-registration
POST   /api/auth/login               # Login with email+password → JWT
POST   /api/auth/refresh             # Refresh expired JWT
POST   /api/auth/logout              # Invalidate refresh token
POST   /api/auth/forgot-password     # Send password reset email
POST   /api/auth/reset-password      # Reset password with token
GET    /api/auth/me                  # Get current user profile
```

#### Users / Employees
```
GET    /api/users                     # List all employees (admin)
GET    /api/users/:id                 # Get employee by ID
POST   /api/users                     # Create employee (admin)
PUT    /api/users/:id                 # Update employee (admin/self)
DELETE /api/users/:id                 # Soft-delete employee (admin)
GET    /api/users/:id/leaves          # Get employee's leave history
GET    /api/users/:id/balance         # Get employee's leave balance
PATCH  /api/users/:id/avatar          # Upload profile picture
```

#### Departments
```
GET    /api/departments               # List all departments
POST   /api/departments               # Create department (admin)
PUT    /api/departments/:id           # Update department (admin)
DELETE /api/departments/:id           # Delete department (admin)
GET    /api/departments/:id/employees # List employees in department
```

#### Leave Requests
```
GET    /api/leaves                    # List leaves (filtered by role)
GET    /api/leaves/:id                # Get leave details
POST   /api/leaves                    # Submit leave request
PUT    /api/leaves/:id                # Edit leave (if still pending)
DELETE /api/leaves/:id                # Cancel leave (if still pending)
PATCH  /api/leaves/:id/approve        # Approve leave (manager/admin)
PATCH  /api/leaves/:id/reject         # Reject leave + reason (manager/admin)
GET    /api/leaves/calendar           # Get calendar view data
GET    /api/leaves/export             # Export to CSV/PDF
```

#### Leave Policies
```
GET    /api/policies                  # List all leave policies
POST   /api/policies                  # Create policy (admin)
PUT    /api/policies/:id              # Update policy (admin)
DELETE /api/policies/:id              # Delete policy (admin)
GET    /api/policies/:id/rules        # Get policy rules (accrual, carry)
```

#### Holidays
```
GET    /api/holidays                  # List company holidays
POST   /api/holidays                  # Add holiday (admin)
PUT    /api/holidays/:id              # Update holiday (admin)
DELETE /api/holidays/:id              # Delete holiday (admin)
```

#### Notifications
```
GET    /api/notifications             # User's notifications
PATCH  /api/notifications/:id/read    # Mark as read
PATCH  /api/notifications/read-all    # Mark all as read
DELETE /api/notifications/:id         # Delete notification
```

#### Reports / Analytics
```
GET    /api/reports/summary           # Company-wide leave summary
GET    /api/reports/department/:id     # Department-wise report
GET    /api/reports/trend             # Leave trend over time
GET    /api/reports/balance           # All employee balances
GET    /api/reports/export            # Export report (CSV/PDF)
```

#### AI Endpoints
```
POST   /api/ai/predict-peak           # Predict peak leave periods
POST   /api/ai/suggest-dates          # Suggest optimal leave dates
POST   /api/ai/chatbot                # AI assistant for leave queries
GET    /api/ai/anomalies              # Detect unusual leave patterns
GET    /api/ai/insights               # AI-generated leave insights
```

