## 5. Frontend Enhancements Roadmap

### 5.1 Current Frontend Improvements Needed

| Area | Current State | Target State |
|------|--------------|--------------|
| **State Management** | Single `AppContext` with everything | Split contexts OR use Zustand/TanStack Query |
| **API Layer** | Mock data imports | Axios instance + React Query for caching/mutations |
| **Error Handling** | None | React Error Boundaries + global error handler |
| **Loading States** | None | Skeleton screens + Suspense boundaries |
| **Forms** | Manual validation | React Hook Form + Zod schemas |
| **Routing** | Basic 3 routes | 15+ routes with lazy loading |
| **Mobile** | Sidebar broken | Responsive sidebar (hamburger on mobile) |
| **Tables** | No pagination | Server-side pagination + sorting + column resize |
| **Theme** | Dark only | Dark + Light theme toggle |
| **Accessibility** | None | ARIA labels, keyboard navigation, screen reader |
| **Icons** | Inline SVGs | Lucide React icon library |
| **Dates** | Raw strings | date-fns / dayjs formatting |
| **Charts** | None | Recharts / Chart.js for analytics |
| **File Upload** | None | react-dropzone for document upload |

