## 8. Security & Production Hardening

### 8.1 Security Checklist

| # | Item | Implementation |
|---|------|---------------|
| 1 | **Password Hashing** | bcrypt with salt rounds ≥ 12 |
| 2 | **JWT Tokens** | Short-lived access (15min) + long-lived refresh (7d) |
| 3 | **HTTPS Only** | TLS/SSL via Nginx or cloud provider |
| 4 | **Helmet.js** | Set security headers (CSP, XSS protection, etc.) |
| 5 | **CORS** | Whitelist only frontend origin |
| 6 | **Rate Limiting** | express-rate-limit: 100 req/15min per IP |
| 7 | **Input Validation** | Zod schemas on every endpoint |
| 8 | **SQL Injection Prevention** | Prisma parameterized queries (built-in) |
| 9 | **XSS Prevention** | React auto-escapes + DOMPurify for user HTML |
| 10 | **CSRF Protection** | SameSite cookies + CSRF tokens |
| 11 | **File Upload Validation** | Type check, size limit (5MB), virus scan |
| 12 | **Environment Variables** | dotenv + never commit `.env` files |
| 13 | **Audit Logging** | Log every state-changing action |
| 14 | **Account Lockout** | Lock after 5 failed login attempts |
| 15 | **Session Management** | Redis-backed token blacklisting on logout |

### 8.2 Performance Optimization

| # | Optimization | Approach |
|---|-------------|----------|
| 1 | **Query Optimization** | Prisma `select` / `include` — fetch only needed fields |
| 2 | **Redis Caching** | Cache frequently read data (policies, holidays, balances) |
| 3 | **Database Indexing** | Index on `user_id`, `status`, `leave_type_id`, `created_at` |
| 4 | **Connection Pooling** | Prisma connection pool (default) |
| 5 | **Frontend Code Splitting** | React.lazy + Suspense per route |
| 6 | **Image Optimization** | WebP format, lazy loading, CDN |
| 7 | **API Response Compression** | gzip via Nginx or compression middleware |
| 8 | **Bundle Analysis** | Vite bundle analyzer to find bloat |

