### 12.2 Frontend File Path Reference

| What | Path |
|------|------|
| Entry point | `client/src/main.jsx` |
| Router | `client/src/App.jsx` |
| Global styles | `client/src/index.css` |
| API calls | `client/src/api/*.api.js` |
| Custom hooks | `client/src/hooks/*.js` |
| Global state | `client/src/context/*.jsx` |
| Shared UI components | `client/src/components/ui/*.jsx` |
| Layout components | `client/src/components/layout/*.jsx` |
| Leave components | `client/src/components/leave/*.jsx` |
| Chart components | `client/src/components/charts/*.jsx` |
| AI components | `client/src/components/ai/*.jsx` |
| Public pages | `client/src/pages/public/*.jsx` |
| Employee pages | `client/src/pages/employee/*.jsx` |
| Manager pages | `client/src/pages/manager/*.jsx` |
| Admin pages | `client/src/pages/admin/*.jsx` |
