## 13. Tech Stack Summary

### Frontend

| Category | Technology | Version | Purpose |
|----------|-----------|---------|---------|
| UI Library | React | 19 | Component-based UI |
| Build Tool | Vite | 8 | Fast dev/build |
| Styling | Tailwind CSS | 4 | Utility-first CSS |
| Routing | React Router | 7 | Client-side routing |
| Server State | TanStack React Query | 5 | API data caching + mutations |
| Forms | React Hook Form | 7 | Performant form handling |
| Validation | Zod | 3 | Schema validation |
| Charts | Recharts | 2 | Data visualization |
| Icons | Lucide React | latest | Consistent icon set |
| Calendar | FullCalendar | 6 | Leave calendar widget |
| Date Utils | date-fns | 4 | Date formatting |
| HTTP Client | Axios | 1 | API calls with interceptors |
| Drag & Drop | dnd-kit | 6 | Drag interactions |
| E2E Testing | Playwright | latest | Browser automation tests |
| Unit Testing | Vitest | latest | Fast unit tests |

### Backend

| Category | Technology | Version | Purpose |
|----------|-----------|---------|---------|
| Runtime | Node.js | 22 LTS | JavaScript server |
| Framework | Express | 5 | HTTP framework |
| ORM | Prisma | 6 | Database toolkit |
| Database | PostgreSQL | 16 | Primary data store |
| Cache | Redis | 7 | Caching + sessions |
| Auth | jsonwebtoken + bcrypt | latest | JWT + password hashing |
| Validation | Zod | 3 | Request validation |
| File Upload | Multer | latest | Multipart handling |
| Email | Nodemailer | latest | Transactional emails |
| WebSocket | Socket.io | 4 | Real-time notifications |
| AI | Google Gemini API | latest | AI features |
| Logging | Winston | 3 | Structured logging |
| Security | Helmet + cors | latest | Security headers |
| Rate Limit | express-rate-limit | latest | API rate limiting |
| Testing | Vitest + Supertest | latest | Unit + integration tests |

